'''蘿倫·安妮·米勒·羅根'''（{{lang-en|Lauren Anne Miller Rogen}}，{{bd|1982年|7月24日}}）是美國女演員，編劇，演員[[塞斯·羅根|塞斯·羅根]]的妻子。

==早期生活==
蘿倫在[[萊克蘭_(佛羅里達州)|萊克蘭 (佛羅里達州)]]長大。<ref>Serebrin, Tammy (February 2, 2012). [http://www.theledger.com/article/20120202/NEWS/120209872 "Harrison Grad's Film Was Shown at Sundance, Likely Headed to Theaters"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theledger.com/article/20120202/NEWS/120209872 |date=20160304002305 }}. ''[[The_Ledger|The Ledger]]''.</ref> 父母為 Adele Miller 以及 Scott Miller，有一個兄弟，Dan。<ref>Tuschman, Sari Anne [http://la-confidential-magazine.com/living/articles/seth-rogen-alzheimers-hilarity-for-charity "Good Cause: Seth Rogen's Hilarity for Charity"] {{Wayback|url=http://la-confidential-magazine.com/living/articles/seth-rogen-alzheimers-hilarity-for-charity |date=20141220014548 }}. ''[[Los_Angeles_Confidential|Los Angeles Confidential]]''. Retrieved September 7, 2012.</ref> 蘿倫是猶太人。<ref>Schleier, Curt (August 31, 2012). [http://blogs.forward.com/the-arty-semite/162000/ari-graynor-on-jewish-mothers-and-phone-sex/ "Ari Graynor on Jewish Mothers and Phone Sex"] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.forward.com/the-arty-semite/162000/ari-graynor-on-jewish-mothers-and-phone-sex/ |date=20131004224359 }}. ''[[The_Jewish_Daily_Forward|The Jewish Daily Forward]]''.</ref><ref>Fox, Rachel (September 4, 2012). [http://twitchfilm.com/interviews/2012/09/jamie-travis-interview.php "For a Good Time, Call... Director Jamie Travis for a Quickie Chat"] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130204221943/http://twitchfilm.com/interviews/2012/09/jamie-travis-interview.php |date=2013-02-04 }}. [[Twitch_Film|Twitch Film]].</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.jweekly.com/2010/10/22/schwimmers-secret-wedding-another-new-jewish-couple/|title=Schwimmer’s secret wedding, Another new Jewish couple, …|last=Bloom|first=Nate|date=October 22, 2010|work=J. The Jewish News of Northern California|access-date=May 21, 2018|archive-date=2018-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901215710/https://www.jweekly.com/2010/10/22/schwimmers-secret-wedding-another-new-jewish-couple/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

蘿倫畢業於[[佛羅里達州立大學|佛羅里達州立大學]]。在大學的時候，蘿倫認識了室友 Katie Anne Naylon，兩人之後一同編寫電影[[激情熱線|激情熱線]]([[:en:For_a_Good_Time,_Call...|:en:For a Good Time, Call...]])，這是依據兩人的個人經驗改編。<ref>Goldstein, Meredith (August 25, 2012). [http://articles.boston.com/2012-08-25/movies/33339251_1_big-screen-lauren-miller-comedy "Ari Graynor has a lot on the line"] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130119021818/http://articles.boston.com/2012-08-25/movies/33339251_1_big-screen-lauren-miller-comedy |date=2013-01-19 }}. [[Boston.com|Boston.com]].</ref>

==職業生活==
蘿倫一開始出現在許多賽斯羅根的電影擔任小角色，包括[[男孩我最壞|男孩我最壞]](Superbad)，[[淫幕初體驗|淫幕初體驗]](Zack and Miri Make A Porno)，[[購物中心超級警探|購物中心超級警探]](Observe and Report)以及[[活個痛快|活個痛快]]。<ref>Vineyard, Jennifer (August 28, 2012). [http://www.vulture.com/2012/08/for-a-good-time-call-lauren-miller-interview.html "Lauren Miller on Her Phone-Sex Comedy and Being a Struggling Actress Married to Seth Rogen"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vulture.com/2012/08/for-a-good-time-call-lauren-miller-interview.html |date=20191218200617 }}. ''[[New_York_Magazine|Vulture]]''.</ref>

她第一個主演的電影是[[激情熱線|激情熱線]]，與[[艾莉·葛瑞那|艾莉·葛瑞那]]合作主演。[[焦點影業|焦點影業]]在2012年的[[日舞影展|日舞影展]]上以約2百萬美金取得該部電影的版權。<ref>Ryzik, Melena (August 29, 2012). [http://www.nytimes.com/2012/08/30/movies/for-a-good-time-call-finds-humor-in-phone-sex.html?_r=1&pagewanted=all "These Women Don’t Blush While Earning Their Rent"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/08/30/movies/for-a-good-time-call-finds-humor-in-phone-sex.html?_r=1&pagewanted=all |date=20170805021627 }}. ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''.</ref> 並於2012年8月31日在美國發行。蘿倫並同時在[[福斯廣播公司|福斯廣播公司]]的影集[[老媽與奶爸|老媽與奶爸]]裡擔任配角。

==私人生活==
蘿倫在2004年開始與演員[[塞斯·羅根|塞斯·羅根]]交往。兩人在2010年9月29日訂婚並於2011年10月2日結婚。<ref>D'Zurilla, Christie (October 3, 2011). [http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/gossip/2011/10/seth-rogen-wedding-married-lauren-miller-wedding.html "Seth Rogen marries Lauren Miller in wine country wedding"] {{Wayback|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/gossip/2011/10/seth-rogen-wedding-married-lauren-miller-wedding.html |date=20200812194023 }}. ''[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]''.</ref>

